OL,3,CVillagers say wet weather has left
OL,4,Cswarms of midges plaguing their homes
OL,6,FVillagers in Berkshire say swarms of
OL,7,Fmidges are plaguing their homes, and
OL,8,Fthe situation is the worst they've
OL,9,Fever seen.
OL,11,FPeople living in the village of
OL,12,FMidgham are blaming flooding and
OL,13,Fstanding water for the clouds of
OL,14,Finsects.
OL,16,FA vet and horse owner in neighbouring
OL,17,FPadworth says her land has also been
OL,18,Finundated by midges which are
OL,19,Fdistressing and biting her animals,
OL,20,Fand people in Woolhampton are also
OL,21,Faffected.
