OL,3,CVillagers say wet weather has left
OL,4,Cswarms of midges plaguing their homes
OL,6,FExperts say it's down to a mild winter
OL,7,Fand a wet few months.
OL,9,FHorse rider and vet Christel Caderius
OL,10,FVan Veen said: "Since we moved here in
OL,11,Fthe last couple of months, they've
OL,12,Fbeen almost constant.
OL,14,F"We normally only have them for sort
OL,15,Fof 10 to 14 days, but we have had such
OL,16,Fa lot of flooding recently that it's
OL,17,Fbeen fairly well constant.
