OL,3,CVillagers say wet weather has left
OL,4,Cswarms of midges plaguing their homes
OL,6,F"I moved here in the beginning of
OL,7,FFebruary and we've had clouds of
OL,8,Fmidges since. (0:52) And here we are
OL,9,Fmid-April.
OL,11,F"It seems to be much worse than normal.
OL,13,F"I assume it's related to the
OL,14,Fflooding."
OL,16,FSpeaking about the impact on her
OL,17,Fhorses Christel added: They get really
OL,18,Fdistressed, so if they don't wear fly
OL,19,Fbonnets, then the flies get into their
OL,20,Fears and they bite them so much that
OL,21,Fthey bleed.
