OL,3,CVillagers say wet weather has left
OL,4,Cswarms of midges plaguing their homes
OL,6,F"Also, the boy horses particularly,
OL,7,Fthey get bitten on the underneath
OL,8,Faround their boy parts and that gets
OL,9,Freally swollen and painful as you can
OL,10,Fimagine."
OL,12,FThe swarms are a daily spectacle
OL,13,Faround the River Kennet floodplain in
OL,14,FWest Berkshire as they form
OL,15,Fspectacular insect clouds.
OL,17,FThe advice from experts is midges are
OL,18,Fmost active at dawn and dusk so avoid
OL,19,Fthose times.
