OL,3,CVillagers say wet weather has left
OL,4,Cswarms of midges plaguing their homes
OL,6,FAnd if you're out for a stroll, keep
OL,7,Fgoing - midges can't fly as fast as
OL,8,Fyou can walk.
OL,10,FUniversity of Oxford researcher Liam
OL,11,FCrowley said: "The reason why we're
OL,12,Fseeing this huge local increase in the
OL,13,Fnumber of midges, is because
OL,14,Fpopulation is really closely linked to
OL,15,Fthe weather conditions.
